pv -pterabT -i 0.3 -c -N NAME

-p: progress				-r: rate counter
-t: timer (elapsed time)	-a: avg. rate
-e: eta						-b: byte counter
-I: show eta as time		-T: buffer percent

-i SEC: update sec
-N Name: prefix name
-c: use cursor esc sequence instead of CR

-L RATE: limit transfer rate
-B BUFFERSIZE: set buffer size
